{"tid":1893953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張學友新歌為醫護打氣！！！","createTime":"2020-02-23T15:12:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T01:00:53.000Z","uid":125168,"like":11,"dislike":138,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"7de07843c7d9cd474f7a3bdee8ffb25cb1e5a029","tid":1893953,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T15:12:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6LHrVMF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6LHrVMF.png&h=b804689d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n張學友新歌為醫護打氣　承諾以「不添亂」態度防疫　環球點名感謝曾志偉<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Vdtyyi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Vdtyyi&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAyuL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=6ebb901d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2Vdtyyi</a><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎肆虐，接連有歌手用音樂為大家打氣。歌神張學友今早推出國語歌曲《等風雨經過》，並由周杰倫作曲、方文山填詞，為前缐醫護打氣。張學友在MV中承諾以「不自私、不添亂」態度防疫，而唱片公司環球則特別點名多謝曾志偉協助。<br />\n<br />\n今日環球音樂在FB發表了《等風雨經過》的MV，影片主要由<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">內地醫護人員</span></span>的畫面剪輯而成。"},{"pid":"9e69f9db921df6433f3265f84d7e5426eddb07ac","tid":1893953,"uid":125168,"like":79,"dislike":4,"score":75,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T15:13:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/viYKHrW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FviYKHrW.jpg&h=96153473&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"10664d5f7db5210e55ad3195e571604f9f67ed33","tid":1893953,"uid":125168,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T15:15:42.000Z","msg":"不自私、不添亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支那匪語"},{"pid":"fada670dd5ac8a5582c9ebcafbaed4d1c71f3e7b","tid":1893953,"uid":209554,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T15:22:04.000Z","msg":"食屎啦張學友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0df8a788e1b5a1f42f141e283714c7874f30bdb6","tid":1893953,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0